{"tid":585274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【媽聲四起】《環時》總編玩Twitter挑機：你們有生之年都看不到中共垮台！","createTime":"2018-03-08T13:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T09:04:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"cac47df420a924c76263ee0855870421a11bba2e","tid":585274,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/huxijin1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fhuxijin1.jpg&h=c6c98841&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國的網絡長城一直將Facebook、Twitter等「外國勢力」拒諸門外，但中國的官媒卻似乎享有特權。最近《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進最近卻在Twitter開設中文帳號，吸引了超過1萬名網友追蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-08-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.39.18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-08-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.39.18.jpg&h=0bb03013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">部份網友奚落胡錫進：「以前在牆內拿你沒辦法，來牆外了，要你好看。」</span>胡則不忘替中國共產黨辯護，跟網民打賭稱他們有生之年看不到共產黨垮台。胡更表示西方近年褒獎中國的異見人士，正正反映出中國日益強大，異見人士才有利用價值。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-08-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.39.36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-08-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.39.36.jpg&h=30cc0aa7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《環時》是中國的官媒，文章緊隨中共立場，並宣揚民族主義。然而，胡錫進也曾表示遭到官方施壓，收到上頭領導針對某則報道的禁令。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/%E8%9E%A2%E5%B9%95%E5%BF%AB%E7%85%A7-2018-03-08-%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%8811.41.26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7-2018-03-08-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%258D%258811.41.26.jpg&h=e9ec162e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/03/08/article/55578/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F03%2F08%2Farticle%2F55578%2F&d=daZih1SojmXJgy%2BEusdGXQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=f5c8d2c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/03/08/article/55578/</a>"},{"pid":"18c87733afbabe32dee294f6e7068a07bb97397c","tid":585274,"uid":55533,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n愛國人士用外國勢力野"},{"pid":"2e0c8c236290a2d62dbaa77e918bcced049222c4","tid":585274,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:36:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8260acdfe6df6ec2b7c07255edce42fece86a44c","tid":585274,"uid":25858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:37:59.000Z","msg":"咁支那就俾佢燈死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bce2378dfd7aac27fd8354fbb96e1b289b90e51","tid":585274,"uid":61280,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T13:38:49.000Z","msg":